title: Bread Tabs or Clips Or Tags
name: Bread Tabs or Clips Or Tags
description:
A Map by Ninabarbuto

Where do you find bread tabs? I am mapping where people find them on the street and where they come from. If you want you can add grocery stores too but I rather it be the bread manufactures than that. But please if you find a bread tab on the street pick it up and photo graph it and map it.  Thanks this if for a project that will grow. for more info:
ninamariebarbuto.blogspot.com

thanks
